name: Mean Mister Mustard
description:
Mixed media painting over some kind of plastic-paper material (I guess it's a light difusor) took from a led tv screen.

The original art has 110 x 60 cm (about 43.5 x 23.5 in) and the NFT version has 2797  x 4956 pixels at 240 dpi.

The first buyer of this piece will receive the physical version, international shipping included.
